Muriel Ostriche https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Muriel_Ostriche 0 Muriel Ostriche (24 May 1896, New York City - 3 May 1989, St Petersburg, Florida) was an American silent film actress. She was also the face of Moxie. She was signed by the Thanhouser Company based in New Rochelle, New York and starred in 134 films in her career.
